## 2026-03-07 - US-012
- Created `game/hooks/..."
`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
- The `mousemove` guard `document.pointerLockElement !== canvas` is not just a best-practice — without it, every page-level mouse movement would rotate the camera, making the game unplayable even when not in pointer lock mode
- Mouse sensitivity `0.002` (rad/pixel) is a commonly tuned value for FPS games; it means moving the mouse 500 pixels does one full 180° sweep — configuring it in `grid.json` lets game designers tune it without touching code
`─────────────────────────────────────────────────`

